parameters.name: DestinationCidrBlock
parameters.description: The destination CIDR block of the route entry, supporting both IPv4 and IPv6 segments.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The number of entries to display per batch query. Range: **1**~**500**, default value is **50**.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description:
Indicates whether there is a token for the next query. Values:
- If **NextToken** is empty, it means there is no next query.
- If **NextToken** has a return value, this value indicates the token for the start of the next query.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The ID of the region where the instance is located.

parameters.name: RouteTableId
parameters.description: The ID of the route table.

parameters.name: TargetInstanceId
parameters.description: The ID of the route publishing target instance.

parameters.name: TargetType
parameters.description: The type of the route publishing target.
